            <title>极摩客 EVO-X1 迷你主机上架：锐龙 AI 9 HX 370 处理器，5299 元</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/810/518.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/810/518.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 07:16:03 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D2029428" rel="nofollow">华南吴彦祖</a> 的线索投递！</div>
